<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6557095>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–6. Tarsobaenus letourneauae, n. sp. (paratypes): 1—dorsal habitus; 2—head; 3—male, ventral abdomen; 4—female, ventral abdomen; 5—elytral plica; 6—lateral habitus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6557095/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6557097>
    dc:description "FIGURES 7–11. Tarsobaenus piper, n. sp. (holotype, paratype): 7—holotype, dorsal habitus; 8—head; 9—paratype, dorsal habitus; 10—elytral plica; 11—lateral habitus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6557097/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6557101>
    dc:description "FIGURES 12–16. Tarsobaenus hansoni, n. sp. (holotype, paratype): 12—holotype, dorsal habitus; 13—head; 14—paratype, dorsal habitus; 15—elytral plica; 16—lateral habitus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6557101/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

